<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Following my previous email and associated correspondence from </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Close Brothers Premium Finance</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">, they have informed us that they </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">have cancelled your premium finance agreement</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">. This is due to Close Brothers being unable conduct the required due diligence checks.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br><b>Your insurance remains in place</b></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">. However, </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Close Brothers will begin debt collection proceedings in respect of the outstanding balance</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Please contact us to discuss this on </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> where we can outline your options and provide information and assistance.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Customer Accounts Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>